## Coding Conventions
- Use `python-dotenv` to load all secrets from `.env`
- Never hardcode API keys, tokens, or credentials
- All database queries go through `src/db.py` вЂ” no raw SQL elsewhere
- Use `loguru` for logging (not print statements)
- Every function must have a docstring
- Handle all API errors with try/except and log the full error
- Retry failed external calls up to 3 times with exponential backoff
- Minimum 3-second delay between Shopee scrape requests

## Environment Variables (in .env)
```
SUPABASE_URL=
SUPABASE_KEY=
